# Strict ToyC-compatible subset of the imported SysY test cases.
#
# Excluded for now:
# - lv1 octal/hex literals: ToyC NUMBER is decimal only.
# - lv4-lv8 cases with uninitialized or multi-name declarations.
# - lv8 cases using SysY runtime I/O functions.
# - lv9 and perf cases using arrays and SysY runtime helpers.
